      Mastered by Andrei “Ony” Eremin in Philadelphia.</small></p>

      <p><small>Thank you for listening.<br />
      <a href="http://twitter.com/wearebrightly">@wearebrightly</a> / wewerebrightly.com</small></p>
    </Prose>
  </div>
</CaseStudyLayout>
